<L>__{exterior dalai lama's residence, norbulinka day}
<A>__{they have reached the residence. the boy's mother caresses his little head.}
<C>__{mother}
<D>__{i turn you over again, today, lhamo. one day, you will not be able to come running to us.}
<C>__{tenzin gyatso}
<D>__{but you will always be here?}
<C>__{mother}
<D>__{me?}
<C>__{tenzin gyatso}
<D>__{you will always!}
<C>__{mother}
<D>__{i have one more piece of news. a baby is coming.}
<A>__{tenzin grabs at her stomach and shrieks with laughter.}
<C>__{tenzin gyatso}
<D>__{oh, mama! who will it be?}
<A>__{the mother places her hands on tenzin gyatso's.}
<C>__{mother}
<D>__{oh, no! who can it be?}
<A>__{a string of old monks, stand, waiting for the naughty boy.}
